title: A more interesting animation app, good interaction details
text:
"Dancing Particle" is an Apple Ios App that can dynamically synthesize wallpapers. It has more than 50 dynamic particle effects, each of which can generate wallpapers. You can download it in appstore.

App Name: Dancing Particle
